'''律师过剩'''（{{lang-en|Overlawyered}}）是一个关于[[美国|美国]]法律系统的[[博客|博客]]<ref name="Not enough lawyers">{{cite news|url=https://www.economist.com/united-states/2011/09/03/not-enough-lawyers|title=Barriers to entry in the legal profession - Not enough lawyers|date=Sep 3, 2011|website=[[The_Economist|The Economist]]|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2021-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508042934/https://www.economist.com/united-states/2011/09/03/not-enough-lawyers|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由{{le|沃尔特·奥尔森|Walter Olson}}（Walter Olson）创办和运营，以{{le|侵权法改革|Tort reform}}（Tort Reform）为主题，于1999年成立<ref>{{cite book|title=Law Institute Journal: The Official Organ of the Law Institute of Victoria|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zdg5AQAAIAAJ|year=2002|publisher=Reviews Pty. Limited|pages=30-|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808234422/https://books.google.com/books?id=zdg5AQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{le|Law.com}}称其为“被广泛认为是最古老的法律博客，也是最受欢迎的博客之一”<ref name=lawcom>{{cite news|url=http://www.law.com/jsp/legaltechnology/pubArticleLT.jsp?id=1202426527551|publisher=[[Law.com|Law.com]]|title=How to Build a Better Law Blog|author=C.C. Holland|date=2008-12-08|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2009-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090712075036/http://www.law.com/jsp/legaltechnology/pubArticleLT.jsp?id=1202426527551|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

许多[[美国人|美国人]]觉得美国“律师过剩”，然而[[布鲁金斯学会|布鲁金斯学会]]的克利福德·温斯顿（Clifford Winston）和罗伯特·克兰德尔（Robert Crandall）以及[[休斯敦大学|休斯敦大学]]的维克拉姆·马赫什里（Vikram Maheshri）认为，事实上美国的问题在于“律师过少”，而不是“律师过剩”。他们在一本书中指出，在过去几十年里，美国严格的[[律师准入制度|律师准入制度]]人为地将律师数量控制在一个较低的水平。律师人数过少，再加上从政律师对经济的过分管控，使得律师们在工资之外有一笔不劳而获的额外收入<ref name="Not enough lawyers"/>。

律师过剩的主题是揭露[[美国|美国]][[侵权法|侵权法]][[制度|制度]]的荒唐<ref name=courttv>{{cite news|url=http://www.courttv.com/news/cow/072501_overlawyered_ctv.html|publisher=Court TV|title=Chasing the Ambulance Chasers|author=Adrien Seybert|date=2001-07-25|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080830021417/http://www.courttv.com/news/cow/072501_overlawyered_ctv.html|archive-date=2008-08-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、过度<ref name="forbes">{{cite news|publisher=Forbes|title=Seventh-Amendment Follies|author=William Baldwin|url=https://www.forbes.com/forbes/2005/0411/020.html|date=2005-04-11|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516142037/https://www.forbes.com/forbes/2005/0411/020.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及滥用<ref name="lvrj">{{cite news|url=http://www.reviewjournal.com/lvrj_home/2000/May-01-Mon-2000/opinion/13452638.html|publisher=Las Vegas Review Journal|date=2000-05-01|title=Editorial:Our overlawyered society|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2012-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121001151630/http://www.reviewjournal.com/lvrj_home/2000/May-01-Mon-2000/opinion/13452638.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该网站的固定读者包括美国数以千计的[[律师|律师]]、[[医生|医生]]以及考虑建立美国式侵权制度的其他国家的读者<ref name=courttv/>。该网站[[域名|域名]]Overlawyered.com<ref name="BastHawkins2012">{{cite book|author1=Carol M. Bast|author2=Margie A. Hawkins|title=Foundations of Legal Research and Writing|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pBT7CAAAQBAJ&pg=PA307|date=22 June 2012|publisher=Cengage Learning|isbn=1-133-27829-9|pages=307–|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720191353/https://books.google.com/books?id=pBT7CAAAQBAJ&pg=PA307|dead-url=no}}</ref>注册于1995年5月8日<ref>{{cite web| url=https://whois.domaintools.com/overlawyered.com| title=Whois Record for Overlawyered.com| work=[[WHOIS|WHOIS]]| accessdate=2020-07-11| archive-date=2020-07-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711101751/https://whois.domaintools.com/overlawyered.com| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年4月26日，奥尔森宣布该博客已隶属于[[卡托研究所|卡托研究所]]，他则在该研究所担任高级[[研究员|研究员]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://overlawyered.com/2013/04/overlawyered-now-cato-institute-blog|title=Overlawyered: now a Cato Institute blog|first=Walter|last=Olson|date=2013-04-16|accessdate=2013-04-28|archive-date=2021-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211212210052/https://www.overlawyered.com/2013/04/overlawyered-now-cato-institute-blog/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年5月31日，奥尔森在律师过剩官网称，“我于1999年7月1日，在律师过剩发表了第一篇文章，我预计2020年5月31日的这篇文章将是最后一篇文章”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.overlawyered.com/tag/about-the-site/|title=A good run: Overlawyered, 1999-2020|date=March 31, 2020|website=Overlawyered.com|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2021-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211111070937/https://www.overlawyered.com/tag/about-the-site/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

